name: NTT DoCoMo Emoji Set
description:
Ever since owning my first keitai (the classic Panasonic P905i), I've been enamored with the simplicity that was the classic DoCoMo Emoji. So much so, that I took it upon myself to vectorize one of the earlier classic sets.


I wanna say the contained set is from 2000, however given that a lot of online references display the set without any of this initial DoCoMo offerings (like the imode emoji, or other icons specific to Japan).


Since I only included 1 set, I'm open to feedback on updating this file and including more.
